46.03	The_True_Believer	The True Believer	The True Believer: Thoughts On The Nature Of Mass Movements is a 1951 social psychology book by Eric Hoffer that discusses the psychological causes of fanaticism.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/1/1b/The_True_Believer_%28book%29.jpg/300px-The_True_Believer_%28book%29.jpg
